    "description": "《深渊食堂》是一款使用物理引擎的烹饪模拟以及餐馆经营游戏。<br>玩家将扮演一位奇幻世界中的小餐馆经营者兼厨师，体验为顾客制作各种各样食物的过程。<br>游戏主要由接待顾客、制作食物、市场购物三个模块组成。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/9231d927d98325d6b69c289e71112958.avif?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=98 /></span></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>近200种不同的食材<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>十几种味觉和嗅觉，且会随温度而变化<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>顾客不仅点评自己的食物，甚至可能会根据邻桌的食物气味作出评价<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>食物可以被切割加工成任意形状，甚至剔出肉排里的骨头<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>不同种族、年龄的顾客各有自己的口味和语言风格<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>自由设计每一道菜<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>独立定制餐馆的每一个菜品<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>顾客会通过与店主的智能对话来决定要吃什么<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>玩家和自己的steam好友可以一同分享各自创作的美食<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/acd008a006d83c13e315c1e0c68c6751.webp?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/7965e58a5ddeaf8f5f892cb000ac986c.webp?t=1725621676\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/7965e58a5ddeaf8f5f892cb000ac986c.poster.avif?t=1725621676\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=216 /></picture></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/acd008a006d83c13e315c1e0c68c6751.webp?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/66fa5d5f15d58b292804ec8213aa067f.poster.avif?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/66fa5d5f15d58b292804ec8213aa067f.webm?t=1725621676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/66fa5d5f15d58b292804ec8213aa067f.mp4?t=1725621676\" type=\"video/m